Game name document

Top-down, stealth game, vampyres, pixel art

Win condition: Either kill all party goers or turn them to vampyres
Lose condition: (Suspicion fills up,) you burn by sunlight, you take too long sun rises and rooms fill with light

Player:
Movement
Interact with world (objects, party goers)
    Sucking blood has a cooldown and action duration
Batform (Extra)
    Move faster
    Can't interact
    TANK CONTROLS!!!!
    Cause more suspicion

UI
    Suspicion meter
    Party goer dialogues
    Game timer
        Sundial
    Main menu
        Settings
    Progress meter

Environment hazards
    Windows, sunlight
        Can be blocked with curtains
    Punch drink station
        Quench fire after standing in sunlight
    (Garlic bread station)
        Applies damage if eaten, only showup with high sus
    Bathroom
        (Mirrors), party goers go here alone

Suspicion
    Fills in thresholds, more guards appear with higher tiers and bar can't recover below threshold
    The higher it gets, the more guards enter the room

Party goers:
    Movement (kinda flocking behaviour)
    Needs:
        Socializing
        Thirst
        Bathroom breaks
    Suspicion
        Some party goers eat garlic bread when high suspicion, stink lines

Guards:
    No needs, patrols near main areas, suspicion grows fast

Update order
    1. Movement related code
        1a. party goer
        1b. player
        1c. guards
    2. Locator
    3. Player interaction
    4. Lighting system
    5. Suspicion
    6. Party goer behaviour
